text: Anne Søndergaard (born 5 June 1973) is a Danish badminton player, born in Hjørring. She competed in women's singles at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Danish female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Denmark Category:Badminton players at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Hjørring
